data.text:
Who are the top life coaches in the world? This includes the most prominent life coaches, living and dead, both in America and abroad. Be sure to also check these famous motivational speakers and the best books from life coach Brian Tracy. This list of notable career and life coaches is ordered by their level of prominence, and can be sorted for various bits of information, such as where these historic life coaches were born and what their nationality is. The people on this list are from different countries, but what they all have in common is that they're all renowned life coaches.

This list is made up of a variety of popular career and life coaches helping people become successful, including Jay Abraham, Martha Beck, and Lucinda Bassett.

From reputable, prominent, and well known life coaches to the lesser known life coaches of today, these are some of the best professionals in the coaching field. If you want to answer the questions, "Who are the most famous life coaches ever?" and "What are the names of famous life coaches?" then you're in the right place.
